snippet.title: THE MYSTERIOUS DEATH OF HOLLYWOOD STAR NATALIE WOOD - TRUE CRIME TUESDAYS | AMBER HOWE
snippet.description:
Hey Babes!

I'm back with a new video series for my channel. I have always loved true crime and as you guys know I also love makeup so I wanted to combine the two and start a new series called true crime tuesdays. On true crime Tuesdays I will do my makeup will telling you all a true crime story. I just want to put it out their that I didn't make this concept but I felt inspired by content already on Youtube and wanted to put my own spin on it.

Anyway I hope you enjoy this new series on my channel let me know your feelings down below!
